# --- Rust ---
/target/
**/*.rs.bk

# --- Flutter / Dart ---
**/build/
**/.dart_tool/
**/.packages
**/.pub/
**/.flutter-plugins
**/.flutter-plugins-dependencies
**/*.flutter-dev
**/*.iml
**/pubspec.lock

# --- IDE / Editor ---
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
**/*.swp
**/*.swo
**/*~
**/.favorites.json

# --- OS ---
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/desktop.ini

# --- Entorno / Secrets ---
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# --- Claude Code (overrides personales, no se versionan) ---
.claude/settings.local.json
# .claude/memory/ SÍ se versiona: es conocimiento curado del proyecto,
# compartido entre sesiones y colaboradores (no un override personal).

# --- Bases de datos SQLite (runtime, nunca se versionan) ---
**/*.db
**/*.db-shm
**/*.db-wal
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3

# --- Logs ---
**/*.log

# --- Python (posibles scripts aux) ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.venv/
**/venv/

# --- cargo-mutants (artefactos transitorios del gate de mutación, ADR-0133 capa 8) ---
/mutants.out/
/mutants.out.old/
/mutants_gate*/
mutants_gate*.log
